{"tid":1914020,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"App Store 禁止非公認機構 Apps 上架   Apple：阻止武漢肺炎假消息流傳","createTime":"2020-03-07T08:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T05:53:13.000Z","uid":344307,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f78f8734adec4b6fc90e40eebc45f90459848472","tid":1914020,"uid":344307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"CNBC 日前發表報告，透露 Apple 為防止有關武漢肺炎的錯誤資訊傳播，拒絕所有不是來自「公認機構」的 Apps 上架。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nCNBC 和 4 位獨立開發者進行訪談，他們各自都有被 App Store 拒絕上架的 Apps，而這些 Apps 的內容都是和武漢肺炎有關，有一些是以地圖顯示確診患者的全球分佈情況。Apple 曾經通過電話告訴開發商，任何和武漢肺炎有關的東西，都必須由官方衛生組織或政府發布。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n現時在&nbsp;App Store&nbsp;搜索和武漢肺炎相關的 Apps，發現的結果很少，其中包括巴西政府發布的一個&nbsp;App。Apple&nbsp;一直在評估有關武漢肺炎的&nbsp;Apps，防止錯誤的消息傳播；知情人士更指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">Apple&nbsp;會視乎開發者是否代表用戶可以信任的組織，例如政府或關注健康的組織，以發布準確的數據。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇?"},{"pid":"367cb8fd7ba10ab5a2bdc9f19b24a657915bfb6e","tid":1914020,"uid":201182,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"姐係香港政府同WHO既app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人整個D都可以byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1ce81b2a1fa4257addd66be12a4c9217b43fb7","tid":1914020,"uid":249979,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"Apple: China's money is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56765aa3a03c7596a77979397c1fd9d6b3b1d78","tid":1914020,"uid":6313,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"Ifan連蘋果維穩都會話無問題<br />\n慢慢變成支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618884f0d8dd4bc91dc6200102c8f72d39a710e4","tid":1914020,"uid":266503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"侵侵何時對付華爾街 Apple google 奶共"},{"pid":"a995