":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b24fee3f155b307de703a7c607d49d44df14f73","tid":1914020,"uid":226155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"Google SEARCH 直接將 武漢肺炎 coronavirus之類Link去<br />\nSOS Alert：COVID-19<br />\n再用WHO資料<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：GOOGLE無奶共，Apple先奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"2間都奶共 唔洗爭啦 <br />\n依加睇下邊間會改善先啦"},{"pid":"7f5ee6ac70b92cbf14e02257e8a2bd7c076675f6","tid":1914020,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e2e35905f8c7ab71308613d17ac30f9650131e","tid":1914020,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"相信政府<br />\n無事<br />\n身體健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1daa56e68155f995e90f67303a41f0d20f9960ae","tid":1914020,"uid":68772,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9952f8191954f75fff6697bbceb665a5ade89ca","tid":1914020,"uid":344307,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"我就覺得任何關於Apple嘅嘢都disproportionally overblown&nbsp;By Vintage<br />\n<br />\nVintage哥你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地應該相信支那既消息 相信WHO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"見你咁唔了解時事 俾兩篇嘢你睇<br />\n<br />\n第一篇：<br />\nGoogle Play hides search results for &lsquo;coronavirus&rsquo; Android apps<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Searching for &ldquo;coronavirus&rdquo; or &ldquo;COVID-19&rdquo; on the Play Store app or <a href=\"http://play.google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=3f6b94da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">play.google.com</a> this evening returns a &ldquo;no results found&rdquo;</span> message for Android apps and games. Similar terms<br />\n<br />\nOther tech companies have taken similar steps to prevent the spread of misinformation. Facebook and Twitter have banned misleading coronavirus-related ads, and Amazon has banned coronavirus products and sellers attempting to price gouge on items like face masks and hand sanitizer. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5google.com/2020/03/03/google-play-coronavirus-android-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5google.com%2F2020%2F03%2F03%2Fgoogle-play-coronavirus-android-search%2F&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e4064e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://9to5google.com/2020/03/03/google-play-coronavirus-android-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二篇：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Searches for coronavirus and &zwnj;COVID-19&zwnj; on the App Store</span> bring up few results, including a &zwnj;COVID-19&zwnj; virus tracker from Healthlynked that uses World Health Organization data, <span style=\"color: red;\">the Epoch Times</span>, and an app from the Brazilian government. <br />\n&gt;&gt;優先出大紀元喎 用返你地邏輯 唔知又係咪代表Apple「暗黃」呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Other tech companies have taken similar steps to prevent the spread of misinformation.</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook</span> and <span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter</span> have banned misleading coronavirus-related ads, and <span style=\"color: red;\">Amazon</span> has banned coronavirus products and sellers attempting to price gouge on items like face masks and hand sanitizer. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Google</span> also has a policy against apps that capitalize on a natural disaster or profit from a tragic event and there are <span style=\"color: red;\">no apps related to the coronavirus available from Google Play in the United States.</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2020/03/05/apple-cracking-down-coronavirus-apps/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2Fapple-cracking-down-coronavirus-apps%2F&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=609421f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.macrumors.com/2020/03/05/apple-cracking-down-coronavirus-apps/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解我未見到有人開po講Google, Twitter, Facebook, Amazon？<br />\n呢個po入面都冇喎 點解嘅點解嘅？</span>"},{"pid":"6924f5562bbf4e66085bccba3528125236ba89f4","tid":1914020,"uid":68772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a72d6512c7b9655ba236929ff764eb3f4aa5ee16","tid":1914020,"uid":9387,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9952f8191954f75fff6697bbceb665a5ade89ca","tid":1914020,"uid":344307,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"我就覺得任何關於Apple嘅嘢都disproportionally overblown&nbsp;By Vintage<br />\n<br />\nVintage哥你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地應該相信支那既消息 相信WHO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"見google識黃標<br />\napple都不甘落後 加推呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"你兩個又再次一齊出現互相附和 乜真係咁啱呀 點解嘅點解嘅？"},{"pid":"be4f84c007158660160f24394247d07dd19dd9bb","tid":1914020,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"APPLE真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"55b9c9fcc3e3cf198ec2e81fb1d7